Capstone



 





Specializing in trading volatility as an asset class





Capstone Investment Advisors is a global fund manager that has specialized in trading volatility as an asset class since its inception in 2007. Capstone currently manages approximately $4.8 billion (as of July 1, 2017) in assets primarily for pensions, endowments, and foundations. The assets are managed across two platforms: a volatility arbitrage fund and customized volatility-based investment solutions. Capstone is headquartered in New York and has an office in London.




